<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Solo HQ Early Creator Reward</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --blue: #0056FF;
      --blue-light: #EEF4FF;
      --text: #111827;
      --subtext: #6B7280;
      --bg: #F7F8FA;
      --card: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #E5E7EB;
      --warning-bg: #FFF7ED;
      --warning-text: #9A3412;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 16px 48px;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 28px 22px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #EAF1FF 0%, #FFFFFF 72%);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #DFE8FF;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(0, 86, 255, 0.08);
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 29px;
      line-height: 1.22;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .card {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 22px;
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin: 7px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .steps {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #F9FAFB;
      border: 1px solid #EEF0F3;
    }

    .num {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .step-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 2px;
    }

    .step-desc {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--subtext);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .email-box {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--blue-light);
      border: 1px solid #DCE6FF;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-weight: 800;
      word-break: break-all;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .button {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .warning {
      background: var(--warning-bg);
      border-color: #FED7AA;
      color: var(--warning-text);
    }

    .warning h2 {
      color: var(--warning-text);
    }

    .muted {
      color: var(--subtext);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 28px;
      color: var(--subtext);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .page {
        padding: 20px 14px 40px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 24px 20px;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="tag">Early Creator Reward</div>
      <h1>Share Your Solo HQ Workflow and Apply for 1 Year of Founder Plan</h1>
      <p>
        Solo HQ has just launched. We are offering a limited number of 1-year Founder Plan offer codes to early users who share their real workflow.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>How to participate</h2>
      <p>
        Share a public post about Solo HQ on X, YouTube, TikTok, Reddit, Product Hunt, Indie Hackers, Instagram, Threads, or any other public platform.
      </p>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="num">1</div>
          <div>
            <p class="step-title">Share your real workflow</p>
            <p class="step-desc">Post screenshots, a short demo video, a tutorial, or a workflow breakdown showing how you use Solo HQ.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="num">2</div>
          <div>
            <p class="step-title">Send us the link</p>
            <p class="step-desc">After publishing, send your content link or screenshots to the email below.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="num">3</div>
          <div>
            <p class="step-title">Wait for confirmation</p>
            <p class="step-desc">After manual confirmation, qualified users will receive an App Store Offer Code.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Content ideas</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>How I manage my solo business with Solo HQ</li>
        <li>My project, task, and finance workflow as a freelancer</li>
        <li>A quick demo of Solo HQ for indie makers</li>
        <li>How I track income, expenses, and project progress in one place</li>
        <li>Why I wanted one workspace for projects, tasks, and finances</li>
        <li>What works well in Solo HQ and what could be improved</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Content guidelines</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Show a real Solo HQ use case.</li>
        <li>Posts can be screenshots, short videos, written posts, tutorials, or workflow breakdowns.</li>
        <li>For written posts, we recommend at least 80 words.</li>
        <li>You may include what works, what feels unclear, or what could be improved.</li>
        <li>Positive feedback is not required.</li>
        <li>Fixed wording is not required.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>What you can receive</h2>
      <p>
        Qualified content may receive a <strong>1-year Founder Plan offer code</strong>. Codes are limited and available on a first-come, first-served basis.
      </p>
      <p>
        Founder Plan includes:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Unlimited projects</li>
        <li>Unlimited finance records</li>
        <li>Full finance statistics</li>
        <li>Full business analytics</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>How to apply</h2>
      <p>
        After publishing, send your content link or screenshots to:
      </p>

      <div class="email-box">
        quietbyte188@gmail.com
      </div>

      <a class="button" href="mailto:quietbyte188@gmail.com?subject=Solo%20HQ%20Early%20Creator%20Reward%20Application">
        Send Email
      </a>

      <p class="muted">
        We recommend including the platform, content link, screenshots, and your contact email in the message.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card warning">
      <h2>Important notes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>This reward does not require App Store ratings, reviews, or positive feedback.</li>
        <li>Positive content is not required.</li>
        <li>Fixed wording is not required.</li>
        <li>Fake content, copied content, or repeated submissions are not supported.</li>
        <li>Offer codes are issued through Apple’s App Store Offer Code system.</li>
        <li>Final redemption, eligibility, availability, and access are subject to the App Store.</li>
        <li>Each user is generally eligible for one code.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <p class="footer">
      © Solo HQ · Contact: quietbyte188@gmail.com
    </p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
